  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Without custom CSS classes, the inserted `div` container is not easily customizable because nothing identifies it.\r\n\r\nI think we should create an [InstantSearch.css](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch-specs) spec for this widget with the following markup:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"ais-QueryRuleCustomData\"></div>\r\n```\r\n\r\nIt would imply adding a `cssClasses` option to the widget, like in most widgets.\r\n\r\nWDYT?",
    "created_at": "2019-03-20T15:42:50Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/3600#issuecomment-474892376",
